      }
    },
    "To export a deck to Hearthstone, create a new deck with the correct class in your collection, then click OK and switch to Hearthstone.\nDo not touch your mouse or keyboard during the import." : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Um ein Deck nach Hearthstone zu exportieren, erstelle ein neues Deck mit der korrekten Klasse in deiner Sammlung. Klicke dann auf OK und wechsele zu Hearthstone.\nBerühre während des imports weder Deine Maus, noch das Keyboard.\nWARNUNG: Dies ist eine Beta-Funktion!"
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "To export a deck to Hearthstone, create a new deck with the correct class in your collection, then click OK and switch to Hearthstone.\nDo not touch your mouse or keyboard during the import.\nWARNING, this is a beta feature !"
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "To export a deck to Hearthstone, create a new deck with the correct class in your collection, then click OK and switch to Hearthstone.\nDo not touch your mouse or keyboard during the import.\nWARNING, this is a beta feature !"
          }
        },
        "es-MX" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "To export a deck to Hearthstone, create a new deck with the correct class in your collection, then click OK and switch to Hearthstone.\nDo not touch your mouse or keyboard during the import.\nWARNING, this is a beta feature !"
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Pour exporter un deck dans Hearthstone, créez un nouveau deck avec la bonne classe dans votre collection, puis, cliquez sur OK et retournez sur Hearthstone.\nNe touchez pas votre souris ou votre clavier pendant l'import.\nATTENTION, ceci est une fonctionnalité en beta !"
          }
        },
        "it" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "To export a deck to Hearthstone, create a new deck with the correct class in your collection, then click OK and switch to Hearthstone.\nDo not touch your mouse or keyboard during the import.\nWARNING, this is a beta feature !"
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "To export a deck to Hearthstone, create a new deck with the correct class in your collection, then click OK and switch to Hearthstone.\nDo not touch your mouse or keyboard during the import.\nWARNING, this is a beta feature !"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "하스스톤에 덱을 내보내기 위해 정확한 직업으로 덱을 만들어주세요. 그 후 OK 누르고 하스스톤으로 돌아가세요. 덱을 읽는 동안 마우스나 키보드를 건드리지 마세요. 이 기능은 아직 정식 기능이 아닙니다!"
          }
        },
        "pl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "To export a deck to Hearthstone, create a new deck with the correct class in your collection, then click OK and switch to Hearthstone.\nDo not touch your mouse or keyboard during the import.\nWARNING, this is a beta feature !"
          }
        },
        "pt-BR" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Para exportar um deck para o Hearthstone, crie um novo deck da classe correta na sua coleção e, em seguida, clique em OK e alterne para o Hearthstone. Não use seu mouse ou teclado durante a importação.\nAVISO, esta é uma funcionalidade beta !"
          }
        },
        "ru" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Чтобы экспортировать колоду в Hearthstone, создайте новую колоду с правильным классом в вашей коллекции, затем нажмите «ОК» и переключитесь в Hearthstone. \n Не касайтесь мыши или клавиатуры во время импорта. \n ВНИМАНИЕ, это бета-функция!"
          }
        },
        "th-TH" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "To export a deck to Hearthstone, create a new deck with the correct class in your collection, then click OK and switch to Hearthstone.\nDo not touch your mouse or keyboard during the import.\nWARNING, this is a beta feature !"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "如果想将本卡组导出到炉石传说中, 请创建一个与卡组英雄对应的新卡组, 然后点击 OK 并切换到炉石传说。\n。在导入过程中，请不要使用鼠标或键盘。\n警告, 这只是一个测试功能!"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "如果想將本牌組匯出到爐石戰記中，請建立一個相同職業的牌組，點擊OK後切換到爐石戰記。\n。在匯入過程中，請不要觸碰滑鼠或鍵盤。\n警告，目前此功能僅為測試功能。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
